      "content": "i tried the tylenol but i think i need something stronger to actually get through the night. my doctor said in the past that sometimes you have to take more than the bottle says if the pain is severe enough. like, if i took 1200mg of the ibuprofen all at once, would that be better than waiting 4 hours for a smaller dose? i just can't deal with this pain right now.",
